OL,3,CPost Office confirms 115 branches to
OL,4,Cclose, with 1,000 workers at risk
OL,6,FThe branches employ around 1,000
OL,7,Fworkers whose jobs could now be at
OL,8,Frisk. Hundreds of jobs are also under
OL,9,Fthreat at the Post Office's
OL,10,Fheadquarters.
OL,12,FThe changes, which aim to boost
OL,13,Fpostmaster pay by #250 million over
OL,14,Ffive years, were confirmed by the
OL,15,Fgroup's chairman Nigel Railton on
OL,16,FWednesday morning.
