OL,6,FHe said the shake-up will also offer a
OL,7,F"new deal for postmasters" by
OL,8,Fincreasing their share of revenue and
OL,9,Fgiving them a greater say in the
OL,10,Frunning of the business.
OL,12,FThe Post Office has 11,500 branches
OL,13,Facross the UK, including 115 Crown
OL,14,FPost Offices found in city centres,
OL,15,Fwhich are staffed by Post Office
OL,16,Femployees.
