OL,3,CPost Office confirms 115 branches to
OL,4,Cclose, with 1,000 workers at risk
OL,6,FSome 2,000 are operated by the
OL,7,Forganisation's partners, such as Tesco
OL,8,Fand WHSmith. Independent postmasters
OL,9,Foperate the remaining 9,000 as
OL,10,Ffranchises.
OL,12,FThe plans, which are subject to
OL,13,Fgovernment funding, would see average
OL,14,Fbranch pay doubled by 2030, with #120
OL,15,Fmillion in additional pay by the end
OL,16,Fof the first year.
