OL,3,CPost Office confirms 115 branches to
OL,4,Cclose, with 1,000 workers at risk
OL,6,FThe announcement follows a turbulent
OL,7,Fyear for the Post Office. The business
OL,8,Fand its former management have been
OL,9,Fsubject to an inquiry about how faulty
OL,10,Faccounting software led to hundreds of
OL,11,Fsubpostmasters being wrongfully
OL,12,Fconvicted.
OL,14,FThe scandal saw the defective Horizon
OL,15,Fsystem give the impression money was
OL,16,Fmissing from their branches, leading
OL,17,Fto some being sent to prison.
