OL,6,FMr Railton said: "The Post Office has
OL,7,Fa 360-year history of public service
OL,8,Fand today we want to secure that
OL,9,Fservice for the future by learning
OL,10,Ffrom past mistakes and moving forward
OL,11,Ffor the benefit of all postmasters.
OL,13,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,14,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,15,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,16,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,18,F"We can, and will, restore pride in
OL,19,Fworking for a business with a legacy
OL,20,Fof service, rather than one of
OL,21,Fscandal."
