OL,6,FBut the Communication Workers Union
OL,7,F(CWU) union called on the Post Office
OL,8,Fto halt the plans and for the
OL,9,Fgovernment to intervene.
OL,11,FCWU general secretary Dave Ward said:
OL,12,F"For the company to announce the
OL,13,Fclosure of hundreds of Post Offices
OL,14,Fhot on the heels of the Horizon
OL,15,Fscandal is as tone deaf as it is
OL,16,Fimmoral.
OL,18,F"CWU members are victims of the
OL,19,FHorizon scandal ` and for them to now
OL,20,Ffear for their jobs ahead of Christmas
OL,21,Fis yet another cruel attack."
